WEBVTT

NOTE Opens at anchor #5

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
[CAPTION: 'CONJURING TODAY']

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:10.000
[A conjurer with fright wig and ping-pong eyes holds a bloodstained saw.]

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:18.000
<v Conjurer>
